      "author": "mei.",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111320887770536428648?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "i was cravings for some mocktail because mocktail is my fav. beverages so my hubby recommended to visit double strain because of good mocktail and i agreed!🥰\n\ni really like the color palette (which is mostly red & green, very contrast and matches with bar)👀💕\n\ni was trying san andreas (4/5) because it has unique aftertaste and trying yellow maru (5/5) and it becomes my favorite mocktail💕🍷\n\nand it has great services too! shout out to great bartenders✨💯",
      "textTranslated": "Saya ngidam mocktail karena mocktail adalah minuman favorit saya, jadi suami saya merekomendasikan Double Strain karena mocktailnya enak, dan saya setuju! 🥰\n\nSaya suka palet warnanya (yang kebanyakan merah & hijau, sangat kontras dan senada dengan barnya) 👀💕\n\nSaya mencoba San Andreas (4/5) karena aftertaste-nya unik, dan saya mencoba Yellow Maru (5/5) dan itu jadi mocktail favorit saya 💕🍷\n\ndan pelayanannya juga bagus! Salut untuk para bartender yang hebat✨💯",
